divs: Sighting DetailsDriving east on Ray Rd, listening to the radio a low level radioactive spill occurred at the intel plant in Chandler, we were both looking off to the South over the intel plant area watching a silver shaped baloon sprire type object moving around their were two objects moving over the plant with movements never seen before, we watched them for a few mins then the took off straight up in the air with incredible speed.
